    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HARUKOHARU</strong> 是一款解谜冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308360/extras/b63b8cdaebb48bdcb283998c82e66dcb.avif?t=1770314985\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ <strong>故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在即将入睡之前，仿佛听见了某个重要之人呼唤自己的名字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回过神来时，发现自己身处一个陌生的空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「啊，你醒了吗？那就请处理一下这个吧。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房间里，刻着各种符号的箱子和方块漂浮在空中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「没关系，不用着急。慢慢来就好。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自称 <strong>Koharu</strong> 的存在让你解开一系列名为 <strong>Recovery Therapy</strong> 的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「不过呢，这些谜题其实解不解都没关系。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就这样，那些曾经想要忘记的记忆，开始渐渐浮现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308360/extras/eb5b7600a4604a44f17da323e8f1b8e1.avif?t=1770314985\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ <strong>游戏特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看似复杂，实际上非常简单的谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带有步行模拟器要素，探索过程中会触发各种事件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过调查物品来推进剧情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有任务指引或时间限制，可以悠闲地游玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即便如此，谜题依然是可解可不解的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据解开的谜题数量变化的多结局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haruko、Koharu，以及你</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**预计游玩时间：**10～60 分钟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4308360/extras/db440a5b206eab45b0d5adf46ebdae4c.avif?t=1770314985\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ <strong>视频直播指南</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论个人或组织，均可在无需许可的情况下进行直播。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
